      <title>美国官员敦促中俄宣布只有人类而非人工智能控制核武器</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-official-urges-china-russia-declare-only-humans-not-ai-control-nuclear-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，一名美国高级官员敦促中国和俄罗斯效仿美国和其他国家的声明，即只有人类而非人工智能才能做出部署核武器的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-official-urges-china-russia-declare-only-humans-not-ai-control-nuclear-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 04:49:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰维持香港最优惠贷款利率于5.875%不变</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-keeps-best-lending-rate-hong-kong-unchanged-5875-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰控股周四表示，在香港事实上的央行维持通过隔夜贴现窗口收取的基本利率不变，追随美联储维持利率稳定的决定后，该公司已将香港最优惠贷款利率维持在5.875%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-keeps-best-lending-rate-hong-kong-unchanged-5875-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 04:27:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>渣打银行利润超过收入增长预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/standard-chartered-q1-profit-rises-55-beats-estimates-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[渣打银行周四第一季度税前利润超出预期，增长 5.5%，原因是利率上升带来的收入增加以及市场交易业务的强劲表现抵消了信贷损失的激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/standard-chartered-q1-profit-rises-55-beats-estimates-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 04:24:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾因南海争端召见中国外交官</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-summons-chinese-diplomat-over-south-china-sea-flare-up-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾周四召见中国外交官，抗议北京在南海有争议的浅滩向菲律宾船只使用水炮，称这是骚扰和“危险动作”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-summons-chinese-diplomat-over-south-china-sea-flare-up-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 04:22:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港央行维持关键利率不变，追踪美联储决定</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-central-bank-keeps-key-rate-unchanged-tracks-fed-move-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港金融管理局（金管局）周四将通过隔夜贴现窗口收取的基本利率维持在 5.75% 不变，以追随美联储维持利率稳定的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-central-bank-keeps-key-rate-unchanged-tracks-fed-move-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 03:21:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>官方媒体报道，中国南方道路塌陷已造成 36 人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/road-collapse-southern-china-kills-36-reports-state-media-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据官方媒体周四报道，中国广东省一高速公路路段塌陷导致车辆坠落，造成 36 人死亡、另外 30 人受伤，当时正值数百万人在该国度假期间出行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/road-collapse-southern-china-kills-36-reports-state-media-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 03:20:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
